79];player=img;\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-5880 aligncenter\" title=\"Planting my Voice\" src=\"http://webdevstudios.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/Post-cropped.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"480\" height=\"480\" /></a></p>\n<p>Dorothy contacted WebDevStudios because she had a WordPress.com website that was not meeting her needs. ¬†She loved the simplicity of WordPress&#8217; admin panel, but felt restricted as to what she could do with it. ¬†We worked with Dorothy to make a great new blog that highlighted her blog posts as well as her beautiful photography.</p>\n<p>We also had the chance to work with some great WordPress products on this project. Dorothy&#8217;s theme was designed using <a title=\"iThemes Builder\" href=\"http://webdevstudios.com/go/ithemes-builder/\">iThemes Builder</a> which makes it easy to create customized website layouts and page templates.  Builder also has some great features for customizing a WordPress website including a layout editor, child theme support, and style manager.</p>\n<p>Her new website is also hosted through¬†<a title=\"Page.ly\" href=\"http://webdevstudios.com/go/pagely/\">Page.ly</a>. ¬†Page.ly provides <a title=\"Page.ly Hosting Plans\" href=\"http://page.ly/plans-pricing/detail/\">amazing managed hosting plans</a> with secured hosting through Firehost.com. They also provide automatic WordPress core, plugin upgrades and nightly backups.</p>\n<p><a title=\"Planting My Voice\" href=\"http://PlantingMyVoice.com\">PlantingMyVoice.com</a> now has a great unique style along with a fully secure and managed home. We love the new website and hope you do too!</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:96:\"http://webdevstudios.com/2011/04/08/plantingmyvoice-com-powered-by-ithemes-builder-page-ly/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_ba